{"tid":328539,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"𡛂姀豼呢d黑猩猩 就是傳播愛滋病比人類","createTime":"2017-07-19T16:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T17:16:07.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7021e060a730235b6a53d853334105cdc7e77a","tid":328539,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"漢恩博士的研究成果發表在最新一期《科學》期刊。研究人員採集1300份野生伊禾比糞便，仔細分析基因組合，證實俗稱愛滋病毒的人類免疫不全病毒（Human Immunodeficiency Virus，簡稱HIV），是由伊禾比身上的SIV演化而來。 <br />\n<br />\n獵人可能在叢林中被野生伊禾比咬傷，或是在宰殺食用獸肉時染病，而帶原的獵人搭船沿著桑加河到了下游的金夏沙，在那裡把病毒傳播給其他人類，進而擴散到世界各地。 <br />\n<br />\n紀錄中最早發現感染愛滋病毒的人是1959年在金夏沙出現，不過學者推測，伊禾比的SIV病毒大概早在75年前就已異變成為愛滋病毒，變成人傳人。"},{"pid":"b740459db6b529fc2493df442c054e32c90e2cab","tid":328539,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:53:26.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"70d0340cfce794c1bd885ead30166edecb4d2f7a","tid":328539,"uid":56634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"被咬傷/宰殺時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ca21575561f2c6656bb8fa9860f28dcecd64f8","tid":328539,"uid":99403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬就係其中一個受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd4368d11225fa15c667e787facd7dea7e1fc01","tid":328539,"uid":99403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10aa131252c4854d6b849335ce688ad295f09d25","tid":328539,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T17:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬就係其中一個受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}